summary: Prodigal Son (FOX) Trailer HD - A fresh take on a crime franchise with a provocative and outrageous lead character and a darkly...
caption: Prodigal Son (FOX) Trailer HD - A fresh take on a crime franchise with a provocative and outrageous lead character and a darkly comedic tone. Malcolm Bright knows how killers think. Why? His father was one of the best, a notorious serial killer called “The Surgeon.” That’s why Bright is the best criminal psychologist around; murder is the family business. He uses his twisted genius to help the NYPD solve crimes, while dealing with a somewhat manipulative mother, an annoyingly normal sister, a homicidal father still looking to bond with his prodigal son and his own constantly evolving neuroses.

summary: Tom Payne, Michael Sheen ed Halston Sage in Prodigal Son, la nuova serie Fox
title: Tom Payne, Michael Sheen ed Halston Sage in Prodigal Son, la nuova serie Fox
body:
Tom Payne, Michael Sheen ed Halston Sage in Prodigal Son, la nuova serie Fox

Fox è pronta a sviluppare il pilot di Prodigal Son, una serie tv prontamente confermata per una prima stagione.

La trama di questo show, che dovrebbe avere l’aspetto di una commedia dai toni Dark, sarà incentrato su Malcolm Bright, un giovane psicologo criminale dotato di percezioni extrasensoriali.

Malcon, tormentato da un padre criminale, da una madre ossessiva e da una sorella…
